# py-aiger-sat
Pythonic interface between AIGs and SAT solvers.

[![Build Status](https://cloud.drone.io/api/badges/mvcisback/py-aiger-sat/status.svg)](https://cloud.drone.io/mvcisback/py-aiger-sat)
